WEBVTT

00:06.470 --> 00:08.239
<I>Previously on "Switched at birth"...

00:08.293 --> 00:09.788
You took home someone else's baby

00:09.789 --> 00:11.527
and another family took home yours.

00:11.528 --> 00:14.265
Does anybody know where
this other child might be?

00:14.266 --> 00:16.664
I'm so glad you found it!

00:16.665 --> 00:19.261
- Who's my father?
- The guy who took off when Daphne was little

00:19.262 --> 00:20.894
and hasn't been in touch since.

00:20.895 --> 00:23.393
Mom, this is Angelo Sorrento.

00:23.394 --> 00:24.954
- Hi.
- Who are you again?

00:24.955 --> 00:27.313
- This is my father.
- You are not welcome in Bay's life,

00:27.314 --> 00:30.102
- you have nothing to do with her!
- We are playing East West Fest

00:30.103 --> 00:31.615
- in St. Louis.
- Awesome!

00:31.616 --> 00:34.001
- Did you know my lawsuit is tanking?
- No.

00:34.002 --> 00:36.078
- But I know something you don't.
- And what's that?

00:36.079 --> 00:37.858
The nurse assigned to our babies that night

00:37.859 --> 00:39.192
worked 48 hours straight.

00:39.193 --> 00:43.121
There is one person who's
always been there for me.

00:43.210 --> 00:44.429
Emmett.

00:48.360 --> 00:50.051
- Bye!
- Road trip!

00:50.052 --> 00:52.587
You didn't want me to be with Liam,
so I broke up with him.

00:52.588 --> 00:54.466
But I'm not giving up on Emmett.

00:57.902 --> 00:59.887
He's moving here.

01:04.566 --> 01:08.184
Angelo... he's moving to K.C.

01:10.733 --> 01:13.132
Moving. Is that right?

01:13.133 --> 01:14.668
Can you see me?

01:14.843 --> 01:16.040
Here.

01:18.000 --> 01:24.074
